[[RAID]] utility on [[linux]] (hint: md = multi device).

### Create RAID 1
<pre>
mdadm --create /dev/md0 --level=1 --raid-devices=2 /dev/sdb1 missing
mdadm /dev/md0 --add /dev/sda1
mdadm /dev/md0 --rebuild
</pre>

